		<abstract>
			<para>



				
MobilityDB is an open source moving object database system. It is based on PostgreSQL and PostGIS. It provides an effective functionality in order to analyze data trajectory. 

Since MobilityDB store a large datasets and treat a complex queries, the scalability is highly required.
In this manual we will see how to make MobilityDB scalable on Kubernetes cluster in order to deploy a portable version of it on AWS cloud plateform.

